# Force git to treat TypeScript sources as text. Some files (e.g.
# src/lib/agents/map/cycle.ts) contain a high density of multi-byte UTF-8
# punctuation (→ — –) in comments, which trips git's content heuristic into
# classifying them as "binary" — making every change an all-or-nothing merge
# conflict instead of a normal line-level 3-way merge. Pinning `text` keeps the
# text merge driver in play.
*.ts  text
*.tsx text
